Minister of Higher and Tertiary Education, Science and Technology Development Professor Jonathan MoyoIn today&#8217;s issue of The Chronicle in a story entitled, &#8220;Parliament summons Professor Moyo to explain Zimdef abuse allegations&#8221;, we reported that the Minister had been asked to explain allegations that he and his deputy Dr Godfrey Gandawa siphoned more than more than half a billion dollars from Zimdef. The correct amount is half a million dollars. The error is is sincerely regretted &#8211; Editor.